WITH CEL_TMP_ERPOrderLineItem AS (
    SELECT 
        "ERPOrderLineItems".*
        , "ERPOrder"."InitialUniqueName"
        , ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "ERPOrder"."InitialUniqueName" ORDER BY "ERPOrder"."VersionNumber" DESC) AS RN
    FROM "ERPOrderLineItems"
    JOIN "ERPOrder" ON 1=1
        AND "ERPOrderLineItems"."ERPOrder_UniqueName" = "ERPOrder"."UniqueName"

)
